public class BinaryHeap<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object

Simple Binary Heap with extract top, bubble up and bubble down operations Objects implementing Comparable can be added To be used for implementing Prim's min spanning tree edge weight comparison
